.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, snowboarding, volleyball, weightlifting, handball
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
House: cape-cod, farmhouse, ranch-style, craftsman, futuristic
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who likes red
2. the person who's sport is swedish is the ranch-style house
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking tea
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the person drinking coffee
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the farmhouse house
7. the person who likes yellow is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the cape-cod house
11. the futuristics house is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the bluemaster-smoker is the person drinking beer
13. the person who's sport is volleyball is the prince-smoker
14. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Sport	|   weightlifting	|    snowboarding	|    biathlon	|    volleyball	|    swedish	|
| House		|     cape-cod	|    futuristic	|     farmhouse	|     craftsman	|      ranch-style	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
